<H2>Welcome to Gardener</H2>
Welcome to Gardener, the offical VTank map editor.<P>

With Gardener, you will be able to:<P>

<UL>
<LI> Easily create a VTank map;
<LI> Upload, download, and manage maps on the VTank game server;
<LI> Cut, copy and paste tiles for quick editing.
</UL>
<P>

Gardener provides tools to help make creating your maps as straightforward
as possible. Specialised dialogs allow quick editing of map attributes,
such as game modes and map properties.<P>

If you have an existing VTank map, you can open and edit it in Gardener.<P>

And of course, Gardener is cross-platform - edit your maps on
Windows, Linux or Mac OS X.<P>

